Description: Commander Erwin sets a plan into motion that will oust the royal government, but if it does not succeed, he and the Survey Corps will be viewed as traitors.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 14
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: The son of a notorious gangster gets caught in a love triangle with his childhood sweetheart and the daughter of his father’s rival.
Title: NISEKOI: FALSE LOVE, VOL. 6
Author: Naoshi Komi

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and helps usher them safely into the afterlife. In this volume, the Soul Reaper captains must stop the invading Quincy army.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 62
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: The demons of Tartaros continue their murderous assault on former members of the Magic Council.
Title: FAIRY TAIL, VOL. 43
Author: Hiro Mashima

Description: A pair of Internet-savvy siblings are transported into a fantasy video game. Can they become the saviors of humanity in this new world?
Title: NO GAME, NO LIFE, VOL. 1
Author: Yuu Kamiya and Mashiro Hiiragi
Contributor: by Yuu Kamiya and Mashiro Hiiragi

Description: A soldier battles aliens over and over on the same day in this adaptation of the science fiction novel, upon which the film “Edge of Tomorrow” is based.
Title: ALL YOU NEED IS KILL
Author: Hiroshi Sakurazaka, Ryosuke Takeuchi and Takeshi Obata
Contributor: by Hiroshi Sakurazaka, Ryosuke Takeuchi and Takeshi Obata

Description: The origins of the Survey Corps leaders Levi and Erwin are told in this spinoff series.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN: NO REGRETS, VOL. 2
Author: Gun Snark, Hikaru Suruga and Hajime Isayama
Contributor: by Gun Snark, Hikaru Suruga and Hajime Isayama

Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 1
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: Ciel and Sebastian finally learn the truth behind the incident of the vanished students at Weston College.
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 18
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: Set in the same universe as “Negima!,” this series follows Touta, the grandson of Negi Springfield, who becomes a vampire after being mortally wounded.
Title: UQ HOLDER, VOL. 3
Author: Ken Akamatsu
